{
  "page": "Rolph Spicer",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Spicer\" title=\"House Spicer\"><img alt=\"House Spicer.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ee/House_Spicer.svg/50px-House_Spicer.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ee/House_Spicer.svg/75px-House_Spicer.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ee/House_Spicer.svg/100px-House_Spicer.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Rolph Spicer</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Spicer\" title=\"House Spicer\"><img alt=\"House Spicer.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ee/House_Spicer.svg/50px-House_Spicer.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ee/House_Spicer.svg/75px-House_Spicer.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ee/House_Spicer.svg/100px-House_Spicer.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Rolph_Spicer_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Rolph Spicer TheMico.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/48/Rolph_Spicer_TheMico.jpg/250px-Rolph_Spicer_TheMico.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/48/Rolph_Spicer_TheMico.jpg/375px-Rolph_Spicer_TheMico.jpg 1.5x, /images/4/48/Rolph_Spicer_TheMico.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Rolph, by TheMico</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">Castellan</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Crag\" title=\"Crag\">Crag</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Castamere\" title=\"Lord of Castamere\">Lord of Castamere</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Spicer\" title=\"House Spicer\">House Spicer</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\">House Westerling</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafrolph_spicer.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafrolph_spicer.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Rolph Spicer</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Spicer\" title=\"House Spicer\">House Spicer</a> and is the <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Crag\" title=\"Crag\">Crag</a> for <a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\">House Westerling</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> He is the brother of <a href=\"/index.php/Sybell_Spicer\" title=\"Sybell Spicer\">Sybell Spicer</a> and grandson of <a href=\"/index.php/Maggy_the_Frog\" title=\"Maggy the Frog\">Maggy the Frog</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rolph_Spicer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Rolph is a square man, with a broken nose and a grey, close-shaven beard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rolph_Spicer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rolph_Spicer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser Rolph serves as <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Crag\" title=\"Crag\">Crag</a>, where his sister, <a href=\"/index.php/Sybell_Spicer\" title=\"Sybell Spicer\">Sybell Spicer</a>, is lady of the castle. With Sybell's husband, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gawen_Westerling\" title=\"Gawen Westerling\">Gawen Westerling</a>, a captive at <a href=\"/index.php/Seagard\" title=\"Seagard\">Seagard</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Rolph yields the castle to <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a>, during the <a href=\"/index.php/Storming_of_the_Crag\" title=\"Storming of the Crag\">storming of the Crag</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Westerling\" title=\"Jeyne Westerling\">Jeyne Westerling</a>, Sybell's elder daughter, treats Robb's wounds after the battle, and the two youths sleep together after Robb learns of the alleged deaths of Robb's younger brothers, <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Rickon_Stark\" title=\"Rickon Stark\">Rickon</a>, at <a href=\"/index.php/Capture_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Capture of Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>. Robb chooses to wed Jeyne, thereby breaking his alliance with <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Sybell begins providing a posset to Jeyne each morning, claiming it will make her fertile.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ser Rolph comes to <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> as part of Robb's retinue when the king departs the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>. When <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Stark</a>, Robb's mother, learns that his <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">direwolf</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_Wind\" title=\"Grey Wind\">Grey Wind</a>, does not like Rolph, she urges that Robb send the <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> away.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Rolph and his nephew, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Raynald_Westerling\" title=\"Raynald Westerling\">Raynald Westerling</a>, are in attendance at Riverrun when Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Karstark\" title=\"Rickard Karstark\">Rickard Karstark</a> is brought before the king after murdering <a href=\"/index.php/Tion_Frey\" title=\"Tion Frey\">Tion Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Willem_Lannister\" title=\"Willem Lannister\">Willem Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Rolph offers his consolations to Robb after the death of the king's grandfather, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Hoster_Tully\" title=\"Hoster Tully\">Hoster Tully</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Robb eventually sends Rolph to deliver <a href=\"/index.php/Martyn_Lannister\" title=\"Martyn Lannister\">Martyn Lannister</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Tooth\" title=\"Golden Tooth\">Golden Tooth</a> in exchange for the freeing of <a href=\"/index.php/Robett_Glover\" title=\"Robett Glover\">Robett Glover</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Robb sets off to the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a> for the wedding of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Roslin_Frey\" title=\"Roslin Frey\">Roslin Frey</a>. Robb and Catleyn are betrayed and murdered by the Freys and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolton\" title=\"House Bolton\">Boltons</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Wedding\" title=\"Red Wedding\">Red Wedding</a>, however.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos51.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>According to a semi-canon source, Rolph and Sybell had conspired with the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannisters</a> to trick Robb into marrying Jeyne.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafsybell_spicer.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafsybell_spicer.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafrolph_spicer.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafrolph_spicer.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> In the aftermath of the Red Wedding, Rolph is raised to the rank of <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lord</a> by the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> and is given the lands and incomes of <a href=\"/index.php/Castamere\" title=\"Castamere\">Castamere</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rolph_Spicer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After resolving the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Riverrun\" title=\"Siege of Riverrun\">siege of Riverrun</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> reminds Sybell that the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Westerling\" title=\"House Westerling\">Westerlings</a> had been pardoned and that Rolph had been named <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Castamere\" title=\"Lord of Castamere\">Lord of Castamere</a>. Sybell reveals that Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a> had additionally promised worthy marriages for her children during their discrete negotiations.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc44.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Rolph_Spicer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />spice trader</td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Maggy_the_Frog\" title=\"Maggy the Frog\">Maggy<br />the Frog